text:
Oh, there's nothing weird about it.
It suits you very well!

Let's take a photo as a memento.
Look this way──

Wearing... this kind of clothes...
It's the first time, so it's embarrassing... but...

Matching outfits with Naa-chan and Chiyuki-san...
I'm happy because of that...!

Yeah, starting Alstroemeria,
with Amana, Chiyuki, and Tenka.

Hehe... Yeah, that's right...
Tenka is... Alstroemeria...!
